description:
Are you a {{chaotic|HOTKEY HATER}}? Good news! you will never have to encounter them ever again.

This mod simply remove {{R|ALL}} hotkeys from various popup UI and conversation UI throughout the game.

If you found any trace of unremoved hotkey, please report to the --

